{"word":"Daughter","slug":"daughter","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Daughter</b> Forbidden to be wife of her mother's husband<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=20&verse=14'>Lev 20:14</a><br/> Sold in concubinage<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=21&verse=10'>Exo 21:10</a><br/> Given in marriage by parents<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=13'>Jdg 1:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=25'>1Sa 17:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=21'>1Sa 18:21</a><br/> Property rights of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=27&verse=11'>Num 27:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=36&verse=13'>Num 36:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=17&verse=6'>Jos 17:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=4&verse=3'>Rth 4:3</a><br/> Used also for granddaughter<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=2'>Gen 36:2</a>"}]}